sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Web as Next.js Frontend
    participant Supa as Supabase Auth
    participant Google as Google OAuth
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant DB as Supabase PostgreSQL

    User->>Web: Click Sign in with Google
    Web->>Web: Generate PKCE code_verifier
    Web->>Web: Store verifier in HTTP-only cookie
    Web->>Supa: Redirect to OAuth authorize
    Supa->>Google: Google OAuth consent
    Google-->>Supa: Authorization code
    Supa->>Supa: Exchange code using verifier
    Supa-->>Web: Session + signed JWT
    Web->>API: API request — Authorization: Bearer JWT
    API->>Supa: Fetch JWKS public keys
    API->>API: Validate signature / issuer / audience / expiry
    API->>API: Check email domain @iemsnewdelhi.com
    API->>DB: Resolve user_account + employee record
    API->>API: Check employee status = ACTIVE
    API-->>Web: 200 OK or 401/403 denied
